All Classes

Class Description
Acknowledgement
The class Acknowledgement provides a model for the server to communicate to the client if the purchase is successfully done or not.
CallbackClient
The class CallbackClient manages the interaction of a client with the server.
CallbackServer
The class CallbackServer manages the interaction between client and server.
Client
This class is used to run a single node in the system.
Client
The class Client defines a client that sends an object to a server and receives its answer.
ClientBroker
This class is used to run a single node and a broker in the system.
GenericClient
This class provides the main methods required to handle interaction.
Offer
The class Offer provides a simplified model to make/read an offer.
Price
The class Price provides a simplified model to make/read a price.
PriceWriterReader
Interface PriceWriterReader of the remote object used by clients and server to communicate their offers and prices.
PriceWriterReaderImpl
Implementation of PriceWriterReader interface.
SendReceiverQueue
This class provides the main methods required to handle interaction between nodes in the system.
Server
The class Server defines a server that waits for a message and then sends an answer.
ServerThread
The class ServerThread manages the interaction with a client of the server.
Subscribe
Interface Subscribe to allow the client to subscribe its remote object.
SubscribeImpl
Implementation of Subscribe interface.
